				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I don't think this is a bad idea but I am not really for it. One thing that does discorage me from this idea is trade skills what if someone deacides to start a skill like tailoring and they need ruined pelts. These pelts are mainly found off of newbie mobs (which is the main reason this skill is great for a newbie to with little cash to start) Now granted they could have started this skill a long time ago when a lower lvl but if they just decided that they wanted to start. For one thing hardly any newbie gathers a bunch of ruined pelts and goes and sells them off there is just no market for them. So what is this high lvl player to do nothing they are screwed because there is no way for him to get it in this area.(Even though alot of pelts may drop off most of the mobs in this area) Now sure there may be other ways for this person to get these pelts but that is only a simple example. Another thing is pets and other requirements for spells I'll take a simple example Bonechips. Easily found off of a low lvl mob the friendly Decaying Skelly. I myself have played a necro and would cast a low lvl pet and send him off to chase these mobs all accross the zone this is a safe and effective way to collect bonechips now with the restrictions the necro has to run out into a zone that may be dangerous for him and fight mobs that are probably just as strong or stronger than the necro to get the chips. This prosses is long and slow with alot of danger and the possible loss of the pet (leading to a loss of bonechips not a gain). Now the necro has another way of getting the bonechips buying them. But bonechips are natually not a part of a vendors selection also the necro is hated by mostly all so that isnt very effective. Last resort buying from other people now yes bonechips are quite easy to find for sale and are relitily cheep but this is only an example and there are alot of other items that are not normally sold by people and also may cost alot. This is my argument and while im not complaining i acctually have no problem with this new system that is likely to arise im just stating the facts.<BR>
<BR>
Laguee <BR>
Warrior of the 13th season.<BR>
<BR>
P.S. sorry that i may have misspelled alot.
