				FARMING. This idea is designed to reduce farming simple as that. For some reason some players see this as a legitimate way to play the game. How does a character get rich in EQ?  Find a MOB that drops a nice item, camp it with a character 10+ levels higher (It is EQ's equivalent of cheat codes.), kill and sell off the item. Little chance of death, no chance for advancement, but plenty of money. If your goal in the game is to get rich then perhaps you ought to be playing Monopoly. 
